  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this tiny RPG, explore the land of Vasto as Twigs the aspiring adventurer. Take on monsters and quests as you search for King Elesio's lost Pippa. Maybe even discover what a 'Pippa' actually is!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grid-based exploration through hand-crafted towns and dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple yet engaging turn-based battle system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short storyline with charming NPCs to interact with and quests to complete</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 1.5 hours of gameplay</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this tiny RPG, explore the land of Vasto as Twigs the aspiring adventurer. Take on monsters and quests as you search for King Elesio's lost Pippa. Maybe even discover what a 'Pippa' actually is!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grid-based exploration through hand-crafted towns and dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple yet engaging turn-based battle system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short storyline with charming NPCs to interact with and quests to complete</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 1.5 hours of gameplay</p></li></ul>",
